{"tid":619301,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"其實d 車鈴向「外」斜有咩實際作用?","createTime":"2018-04-06T13:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T12:42:05.000Z","uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fa4c743f3def5ca0afbae992cdac9190ba3221ed","tid":619301,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:41:43.000Z","msg":"型已經唔型<br />\n咁有咩用其實 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef8ee39cf3b895e6a5d9d1e0ff3c38d2719b69e","tid":619301,"uid":74171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:54:48.000Z","msg":"剩係條鈴向外斜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738af74bfe2c6388a0fac6432c2cb8b78635264c","tid":619301,"uid":19322,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:54:51.000Z","msg":"其實這只是一種改裝風格，俗稱海拉風（hellaflush）。特點就是：一是重心夠低，二是車輪傾角調校，就是我們看到的外八。最大的作用就是在高速轉彎時能夠更好的提供抓地力，防止側傾。前驅車在轉彎的時候有後輪甩尾的趨勢，而向外傾斜那面的外八輪胎因為壓力的作用而全部與路面接觸增加抓地力！如果輪胎是垂直的，轉彎時後輪的兩個輪胎的胎面都不是與路面全部接觸的。"},{"pid":"97e3e76a1cedfe5e3f2df596d6d701a621db59c6","tid":619301,"uid":43953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:57:18.000Z","msg":"唔洗一個月已經要換肽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3505b811e738351aaf3f82adc6b665dec600afa9","tid":619301,"uid":294,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T13:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/215738_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F06%2F215738_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg&h=f6855ecf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0aeb4dac19de25e4eb13c2d1b132fb028dd3e54","tid":619301,"uid":13908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T14:11:08.000Z","msg":"其實原廠車後面都有少少外八"},{"pid":"bc9f5c3f9d644125c693fb182932557d3ac8